creator: SIGMA INTERNET
descriptionHtml:
🥳 Welcome to Muaah!
Muaah is a healthy video chat app for making friends with strangers.
Come join Muaah and start video chat! Discover people you're interested in and connect with new people as you please.

👉 Feature Highlights 👈

✨ 1-on-1 Video Chat
Make new friends in one click. Set gender filters and find your perfect match with a single tap!

✨ Instant Message
Hang up live video chat is not mean the end. You can use text chat to get to know each other deeply!

✨ Save Chat History
Call up old friends and remind of your existence to those who are far away.

✨ Share Your Moments
Post photos and stories on your profile that will attract more attention.

✨Find Fun People
Discover more people you are interested in and video call with them via club channel.

If you need our help, please contact:
📮 hellomuaah@gmail.com

We would love to hear your feedback to make Muaah even better!
